cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.HC 

The paper discusses scholarly e-publishing and its impact on disciplinary conventions, which falls under the scope of digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The analysis of different forms of paper and electronic publications also touches upon cybersecurity (cs.CR) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the paper's focus on evaluating scholarly communication practices aligns with the scope of cybernetics (cs.CY).
